            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "I think the difference in the caveat is referring to the difference between the window scroll lines and cursor move lines. But yeah that could be interpreted differently.\r\n\r\nI think it was originally meant to provide consistency in cursor jump distance, since you can always expect the cursor to jump half a page, independent of the window position.\r\n\r\nEDIT: I tried it on v9.5.0 and it still had the expected behaviour.",
